title: Reversed Virtues
description: I was dropped into a world where the values between males and females were switched!! From a married woman asking me to put it in just once while giving me a fistful of cash, to a female college student offering me her virginity... Is this heaven...? Here begins my journey to get fucked! "What's with this guy...? I've never seen anyone as forward as him before..."
author: Serun
